## Troubleshooting Notes

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| "All ports filtered" on rescan | UFW still blocking from Exercise 2 | `sudo ufw delete <rule#>` |
| Hydra "Connection refused" | Fail2Ban banned the IP | `sudo fail2ban-client set sshd unbanip <ip>` |
| "No route to host" on SSH | Target VM was off/unreachable | Confirm VM is running, re-check IP with `ip a` |
| "Connection closed" after password | Fail2Ban triggered mid-attempt | Unban IP, retry |

